{"tid":2329393,"cid":16,"subCid":0,"title":"隔夜邊爐食唔食得？","createTime":"2020-12-17T08:09:05.000Z","updateTime":"2020-12-18T03:51:41.000Z","uid":3711,"like":43,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":42,"replies":[{"pid":"52d4cdb152db08b298ce35fab0eb895fce60e9bb","tid":2329393,"uid":3711,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-12-17T08:09:05.000Z","msg":"今日去男朋友屋企打邊爐<br />\n過到去坐低 竟然係前一晚打邊爐食淨既野<br />\n個湯底都係原汁原味 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n入面有丸、芝士腸、菜<br />\n上面仲有啲淥完肥牛淨低既油脂漂浮緊<br />\n我問男朋友：乜隔夜邊爐食得架咩......?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n佢話佢屋企由細到大都係咁<br />\n打完邊爐食唔晒就留返第二日再食<br />\n有時仲可以食幾日添<br />\n<br />\n我雖然見識唔多 但隔夜邊爐真係聞所未聞<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n咁我google下啦 搵到既就係：<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span class=\"large\"><br />\n火鍋湯煮30分鐘後亞硝酸鹽含量逐漸增多，肉類長時間高溫烹煮會釋放胺類物質與亞硝酸鹽反應產生致癌的亞硝胺。過夜的火鍋湯中有害物質更多，是不能喝的。<br />\n若食用了過夜的火鍋湯菜可能引起中毒，表現症狀為：頭痛、頭暈、噁心、腹瀉腹痛、嚴重者造成心肝腎損壞。此外火鍋中的嘌呤含量很高，痛風患者嚴禁食用否則容易引起痛風加重。<br />\n出現上述身體不適者，應當停止食用火鍋，有必要的立即去醫院做檢查治療。</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n我嚇到仆街 望住個湯底遲遲不敢起筷<br />\n我驚佢屋企人對我印象唔好 諗住夾硬食<br />\n但都係過唔到自己嗰關 最後裝咗啲白飯就咁食<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n想問下有冇人屋企都係咁架 我平時打邊爐超過個半鐘個湯底已變到好核突<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"70f3a1654a70e363fd1d9350ff005b360123fc81","tid":2329393,"uid":162539,"like":5,"dislike":14,"score":-9,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-17T08:10:04.000Z","msg":"不嬲都係七日鍋先最正"},{"pid":"c1306ba8e811531f2bb4936aa2cfe14935abedb9","tid":2329393,"uid":363208,"like":30,"dislike":1,"score":29,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-17T08:11:38.000Z","msg":"仆街想嘔<img src=\"/assets/faces/cat/unwell.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6542bd766df0874ad7bad673a38ca7ce9a3de04c","tid":2329393,"uid":188907,"like":22,"dislike":1,"score":21,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-17T08:12:46.000Z","msg":"CLS<br />\n淨係d嘌呤都爆錶啦<br />\n比著我扮肚痛食白飯算"},{"pid":"e4f1727a7152031d147cf161f3b992ec59dee8e4","tid":2329393,"uid":373442,"like":24,"dislike":1,"score":23,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-17T08:21:59.000Z","msg":"咁恐怖<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />我屋企最多係未烚既野會留返低，湯底唔會過夜，鍋入面既食物都唔會留"},{"pid":"a872610a0fd76628d87282c0902762e765df7291","tid":2329393,"uid":27416,"like":31,"dislike":20,"score":11,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-12-17T08:31:44.000Z","msg":"你四五手西佢咪又係照食"},{"pid":"8f77cbc3604dd3bc1df8fe8f82a9fc158c6a85d4","tid":2329393,"uid":3711,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"70f3a1654a70e363fd1d9350ff005b360123fc81","tid":2329393,"uid":162539,"like":5,"dislike":14,"score":-9,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-17T08:10:04.000Z","msg":"不嬲都係七日鍋先最正"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-17T08:53:14.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />正 食完即刻中毒"},{"pid":"87433b4a11d1b6f190909abf4d436e7b726ceeed","tid":2329393,"uid":98473,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-17T08:54:15.000Z","msg":"有乜問題<br />\n支那個d海底撈都係咁<br />\n咪又係沒事兒 沒事兒"},{"pid":"61907e01a261628a440caf2c9fd5da800bbafc40","tid":2329393,"uid":3711,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"quote":{"pid":"e4f1727a7152031d147cf161f3b992ec59dee8e4","tid":2329393,"uid":373442,"like":24,"dislike":1,"score":23,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-17T08:21:59.000Z","msg":"咁恐怖<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />我屋企最多係未烚既野會留返低，湯底唔會過夜，鍋入面既食物都唔會留"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-17T08:55:53.000Z","msg":"我屋企都係咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/heard.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />我以為個個屋企都係咁"},{"pid":"913217f5c398f50e2c2786e19bc8585975cf3ec8","tid":2329393,"uid":107620,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"61907e01a261628a440caf2c9fd5da800bbafc40","tid":2329393,"uid":3711,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"quote":{"pid":"e4f1727a7152031d147cf161f3b992ec59dee8e4","tid":2329393,"uid":373442,"like":24,"dislike":1,"score":23,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-17T08:21:59.000Z","msg":"咁恐怖<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/s